articles.title: World fertility rate
articles.description: How the fertility rate changed in the last 60 years.
articles.contents:
The fertility in the 2010s has a step decreasing if comparing with the 1060s. Unsurprisingly high income countries show a lower fertility rate than low income countries. Countries were women have more possibility to have an higher education show that they conceive less child compared to low income.
